Z","msg":"<blockquote>對con去左眼球後面認真快D睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ba7565addb1f1c879e1809d1d8b90bbebbb4ef6","tid":206304,"uid":31847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:47:35.000Z","msg":"試過勁痛，標晒眼水都唔出黎<br />\n最後急急腳入廁所就咁拎水直接沖隻眼沖返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1716e3107340144fbd43e40523578d4820202c22","tid":206304,"uid":3553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"如果走左係眼珠後面應該會勁唔適服架嗨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以前試過走左去後面<br />\n嚇到我，即刻google 點整翻出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a705397eb0bd3da9134beae8956999c778eee05e","tid":206304,"uid":98041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:48:17.000Z","msg":"恭喜佢 要睇眼科了"},{"pid":"ca8fd2f6f52bfcd5e07ff763233955968c2317bd","tid":206304,"uid":28891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>滴眼藥水，合埋眼潤潤佢就得。<br />\n隻con係gel咗喺眼皮，唔會走去眼球後面。</blockquote><br />\n全靠你我係佢眼皮搵返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa68d9ecf7609fc0370f56f495801c12e49a0cf","tid":206304,"uid":12068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:50:36.000Z","msg":"今晚正常訓覺，第二朝就自己係眼角出返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利伸：兩星期一次"},{"pid":"d9466973f9c5e92b19bb38d0994d3036522a1ac6","tid":206304,"uid":2337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T10:51:50.000Z