就一世，佢會結疤、受傷、發炎、結痂&hellip;不斷loop。<br />\n我有個學生就係搞隻con而整傷塊角膜，佢塊角膜會定時反半塊出來&hellip;"},{"pid":"60eb5ffd693c370d71da5f44380bf439c22d197d","tid":206304,"uid":52190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:01:18.000Z","msg":"佢最後都會出返黎 唔使擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申試過幾次"},{"pid":"634f9a3ce7dae360f64e1ba33b4d3b63dca77903","tid":206304,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你知 我知 個單眼佬都知</blockquote><br />\n但係都係冇用嘅"},{"pid":"29a91435b8b566deba7aa2f64e60976fc439ad76","tid":206304,"uid":458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T12:48:48.000Z","msg":"跌左炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申試過隻眼唔舒服又係搵唔到隻con 點知係跌左落地下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}